<div id="pf3ee8" class="pf w5d h2d0" data-page-no="3ee8"><div class="pc pc3ee8 w5d h2d0"><div class="t m8a6 x27 h5 y1d9a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;But now hath he obtained a more </div><div class="t md1b xb7 h5 yecb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">excellent ministry, by how much also </div><div class="t m78b xb7 h5 y1d7e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he is the mediator of </div><div class="t me5c x7c h35 y1d7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a </div><div class="t m85e xa4 h5 y1d7e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">better: </div><div class="t ma1e xb7 h5 y10f7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">covenant, which was established upon </div><div class="t m4a5 xb7 h5 y1c6a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">better </div><div class="t m114e x74 h35 yd3f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promises&quot; (Heb. </div><div class="t m798 x41 h5 y1182 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8:6). </div><div class="t m234 x27 h35 y14ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One of the key ideas of the book et </div><div class="t mb2d xb7 h35 y934 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hebrews is that Jesus and His work are </div><div class="t m2f7 xb7 h35 y1569 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;better&quot; or &quot;more excellent&quot; than a </div><div class="t m2c4 xb7 h35 y110d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stated object. Christ is as much </div><div class="t ma9f xb9 h35 y118c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">superior to the angels as His name &quot;is </div><div class="t ma92 xb7 h35 y1372 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">more excellent than theirs&quot; (1:4, RSV). </div><div class="t m88f xb7 h35 ye68 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through our Lord&apos;s priestly ministry, </div><div class="t m2b6 xb7 h35 y1505 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He has introduced &quot;a better hope . </div><div class="t m17a xb7 h35 y1d37 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through which we draw near to God&quot; </div><div class="t m9d8 xb7 h35 y1194 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(7:19, RSV). Jesus is &quot;the surety </div><div class="t m241 x80 h5 y1194 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of </div><div class="t mb35 x79 h35 y1194 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a </div><div class="t m44d xb7 h35 y12ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">better covenant&quot; (7:22, RSV). His </div><div class="t m750 xb7 h35 ye38 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ministry as a priest &quot;is as much more </div><div class="t m537 xb7 h35 y1407 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">excellent than the old as the covenant </div><div class="t ma87 xb7 h35 y93e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he mediates is better&quot; (11:6, RSV). The </div><div class="t mb7f xb7 h35 y124c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">new covenant is better because it is </div><div class="t m7e0 xb7 h35 y1346 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">based on &quot;better promises&quot; (8:6). </div><div class="t m1581 xb7 h35 y142f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ&apos;s priestly work is carried in a </div><div class="t m5b5 x3 h35 y994 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">`greater and more perfect tabernaci e&apos; </div><div class="t m195 xb7 h35 y156d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(9:11). The heavenly things are </div><div class="t m17b xb7 h35 y14e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">purified &quot;with better sacrifices (9:23). </div><div class="t mb4b xb7 h5 y2cfb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 7 August 8-14 </div><div class="t m15c5 xda h17a y2b08 ff3 fs58 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Heavenly Sanctum)<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
